---
// Module 4: Tech Empowerment & Human Vision
---

<section class="section" id="vision">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="vision-header">
      <div class="section-tag animate-on-scroll">Human Vision</div>
      <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">Technology Empowering Humanity</h2>
      <p class="section-desc animate-on-scroll">
        The Silicon Age is not about replacing humans — it is about amplifying what makes us human. Across three dimensions, technology serves as a bridge to a more equitable, productive, and boundless future.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="vision-grid">
      <!-- Card 1: Knowledge -->
      <div class="glass-card ar-card ar-card-extra vision-card animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="corner-tr"></span>
        <span class="corner-bl"></span>
        <div class="vision-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Knowledge for All</h3>
        <p>Breaking information barriers. Quality education and expert knowledge become accessible to everyone, everywhere — democratizing human understanding.</p>
        <div class="card-footer mono-label">DIMENSION: EQUITY</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Productivity -->
      <div class="glass-card ar-card ar-card-extra vision-card animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="corner-tr"></span>
        <span class="corner-bl"></span>
        <div class="vision-icon icon-magenta">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Productivity Leap</h3>
        <p>As humanity's super-tool, technology multiplies individual creativity and work efficiency by orders of magnitude — unlocking potential we never knew we had.</p>
        <div class="card-footer mono-label">DIMENSION: AMPLIFICATION</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Exploration -->
      <div class="glass-card ar-card ar-card-extra vision-card animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="corner-tr"></span>
        <span class="corner-bl"></span>
        <div class="vision-icon icon-blue">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Boundless Exploration</h3>
        <p>In science, space, and beyond — human-machine collaboration pushes the frontiers of what we know and where we can go. No horizon is out of reach.</p>
        <div class="card-footer mono-label">DIMENSION: FRONTIER</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .vision-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }

  .vision-header .section-tag { justify-content: center; }
  .vision-header .section-tag::before { display: none; }

  .vision-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vision-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .vision-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--cyan-dim);
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .icon-magenta {
    background: var(--magenta-dim);
    color: var(--magenta);
  }

  .icon-blue {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
    color: #3b82f6;
  }

  .vision-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .vision-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-footer {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .vision-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
